        "code": "<div class=\"t4s-text-center\" style=\"padding: 15px 0;color: #fff;\">\n    <div class=\"footer-seo\">\n        <h2>Discover the Future of Open-Ear Audio: NG EarSafe Comm 2.0</h2>\n\n        <p>\n            In a world shaped by isolation and disconnection, choosing the right headphones is no longer just about sound—it's about staying present, safe, and connected. Meet the <strong>NG EarSafe Comm 2.0</strong>, a next-gen solution in the world of <strong>Open Ear Headphones With Mic</strong>, blending powerful functionality with unmatched freedom. Powered by air conduction technology, these headphones are made for those who live, work, and move without compromising awareness or audio quality.\n        </p>\n\n        <p>\n            Unlike traditional earbuds that block the ear canal, NG Comm 2.0 rests just outside the ear, using directional air conduction to deliver sound clearly and precisely. This means you can enjoy music and take calls without cutting yourself off from the world. Whether you're commuting, walking your dog, working from home, or attending virtual meetings, these open ear headphones with mic 2.0 let you stay aware of your surroundings while staying connected.\n        </p>\n\n        <p>\n            What truly sets NG Comm 2.0 apart is its <strong>noise-canceling boom microphone</strong>. Designed for clear voice transmission, this mic ensures your voice cuts through background noise—ideal for remote professionals, online classes, and daily phone calls. Add to that the intuitive mute button, and you’re always in control of your conversations.\n        </p>\n\n        <p>\n            Battery life? We’ve got you covered. With <strong>over 17 hours of continuous playtime</strong> and a super quick 10-minute charge that gives up to 70% battery, Comm 2.0 is built for the long haul. Thanks to <strong>Bluetooth 5.3</strong> and <strong>dual device pairing</strong>, switching between your phone and laptop is effortless. Whether you're streaming music during a workout or hopping on a last-minute Zoom call, the connection remains seamless and stable.\n        </p>\n\n        <p>\n            Built with an <strong>IPX5 water resistance rating</strong>, NG Comm 2.0 stands strong against sweat and splashes—making it perfect for both office hours and outdoor adventures. And with <strong>90% reduced sound leakage</strong>, you can enjoy private listening in public without disturbing those around you.\n        </p>\n\n        <p>\n            Comfort is non-negotiable, especially for people who experience discomfort from in-ear or over-ear headphones. That’s why Comm 2.0 is <strong>incredibly lightweight</strong> and designed for all-day wear without ear fatigue. Its open-ear fit makes it an excellent choice for those prone to ear infections, pressure sensitivity, or hearing issues caused by prolonged in-ear use.\n        </p>\n\n        <p>\n            Use it while you’re cycling, jogging, at your desk, or even during casual evening walks. With the <strong>Call &amp; Music switch mode</strong>, Comm 2.0 adapts to your day, allowing you to shift between productivity and entertainment in an instant.\n        </p>\n\n        <p>\n            In short, NG EarSafe Comm 2.0 isn’t just another pair of Bluetooth headphones—it’s a smarter, safer way to stay connected. Backed by features that matter and designed for real-life moments, this is the headphone you didn’t know you needed.\n        </p>\n\n        <p><strong>Try the new NG EarSafe Comm 2.0 today—experience sound that keeps your ears open and your world within reach.</strong></p>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n    .footer-seo {color:#ddd;padding:30px;text-align:left;border-radius:8px}\n    .footer-seo h2 {color:#fff;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:15px;text-align:left}\n    .footer-seo h3 {color:#fff;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:10px;text-align:left}\n    .footer-seo p {font-size:14px;line-height:1.6}\n</style>",
